{"tid":1130092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指鹿為馬？國家知識產權局：西方國家指摘缺乏依據【冇打擊侵權】","createTime":"2019-04-28T20:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T00:59:12.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d70e4229ec60a113dd2f82b8118c2cfeabe386b7","tid":1130092,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T20:28:57.000Z","msg":"國務院新聞辦公室今日舉行新聞發佈會，國家知識產權局局長申長雨稱，願與包括美國在內的西方國家一道，加強在知識產權保護領域的溝通對話和合作交流，共同打擊各類侵權行為，營造良好的營商環境。<br />\n<br />\n有記者問道，一些西方國家例如像美國，指摘中國打擊侵權無力。申長雨稱，某些國家對中國知識產權保護方面的指摘是缺乏依據的，都是一些大而化之的指摘，更沒有看到中國知識產權保護近年來取得的巨大進步和成就。<br />\n<br />\n申長雨稱，中國在不斷加大知識產權保護力度，堅持對國內外企業的知識產權一視同仁、同等保護，取得了舉世公認的巨大成就<br />\n<br />\n申長雨指出，目前中國還存在一些問題，知識產權局也正在加大力度，繼續努力加以解決；同時，局方認識到知識產權侵權問題是個世界性問題，各個國家都存在，只不過是在不同國家、不同發展階段，有不同的表示形式，不同的程度而已。"},{"pid":"32cc986c39d2bcf30b967710c8c830fc91030400","tid":1130092,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"【冇打擊侵權？】國家知識產權局：西方國家指摘缺乏依據<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190428&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59540351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190428%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59540351&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9Xr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=aad9565c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190428%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59540351&h=33265fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190428&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59540351</a>"},{"pid":"9d75de440ff613331451b86edec324f100153d8a","tid":1130092,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T20:35:56.000Z","msg":"莆田<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9884143c372b240725b7e47e6e38ca857ffa6dbe","tid":1130092,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T20:40:36.000Z","msg":"老屈正版侵犯老翻就有份"},{"pid":"0a2ef5f3aec3c764161900ea555739ea09432fd5","tid":1130092,"uid":42153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T20:54:20.000Z","msg":"抄够咪改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f064194a3543f4279c6a12fb3d7ce4ef99d038","tid":1130092,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T21:58:11.000Z","msg":"痴線架 擺明見到都話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8ed4074fcea19ecf7100fbc982748a3f4f3f90","tid":1130092,"uid":220853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9884143c372b240725b7e47e6e38ca857ffa6dbe","tid":1130092,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T20:40:36.000Z","msg":"老屈正版侵犯老翻就有份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T22:45:50.000Z","msg":"佢成個機構就係咁用之嘛"},{"pid":"9bbfba33b04b0d00d9c8f0a9bfe2a04911fa598a","tid":1130092,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}